    {
      "name": "deposit_v2",
      "docs": [
        "Deposit arbitrary SOL into the pool.",
        "The commitment Poseidon(amount, nullifier, secret) is added as a new Merkle leaf.",
        "Client must compute the commitment off-chain before calling this instruction.",
        "",
        "# Arguments",
        "* `commitment` — Poseidon(3)(amount, nullifier, secret), BE-encoded field element",
        "* `amount`     — Lamports to deposit (must equal tx SOL transfer)",
        "* `memo_blob`  — AES-256-GCM encrypted note (zerok:v2: prefix), stored in tx memo"
      ],
